  "projectName": "terraform-aws-eks",
  "projectDescription": "A Terraform module for creating and managing Amazon EKS (Elastic Kubernetes Service) clusters with support for managed node groups, self-managed node groups, Fargate profiles, EKS Auto Mode, and Karpenter.",
